        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 23. Pleurotoma siebenrocki Sturany, 1900, Station 76 (Sanafir Island, Strait of Tiran, Red Sea). A. Original figure by Sturany (1903). B-E. Holotype, NHMW 84252: front (B), right side (C), back (D), protoconch (E). F. Original holotype label. Scale bars: B-D: 5 mm, E: 1 mm." , "Figure 26. Conus aculeiformis var. torensis Sturany, 1903, Station 88 (El Tor, Egypt, Red Sea). A-C. Figured syntype, NHMW 84223: front (A), right side (B), back (C). E-H. Syntype, NHMW 84224: front (E), right side (F), back (G), protoconch (H). D. Original figure by Sturany (1903). Scale bars: A-C, E-G: 5 mm, H: 0.2 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/118667" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/118673" .

